import { createRouter, createWebHistory } from 'vue-router'
import WebPages from '../views/WebPages.vue'
import Keywords from '../views/Keywords.vue'
import PushConfig from '../views/PushConfig.vue'

const routes = [
  { path: '/', redirect: '/web-pages' },
  { path: '/web-pages', component: WebPages },
  { path: '/keywords', component: Keywords },
  { path: '/push-config', component: PushConfig }
]

const router = createRouter({
  history: createWebHistory(),
  routes
})

export default router
